164
00:10:08,875 --> 00:10:10,291
[SHIHO grunts]

165
00:10:10,375 --> 00:10:11,708
Who're you?

166
00:10:11,791 --> 00:10:14,083
[NAGI] You humans sure are
creatures of convenience.

167
