see what I see up there.

171
00:10:24,916 --> 00:10:26,750
[SHIHO gasps]

172
00:10:26,833 --> 00:10:28,541
[NAGI]
The HiME Star.

173
00:10:28,625 --> 00:10:31,083
--[SHIHO whimpers]
