244
00:13:43,291 --> 00:13:45,833
I just don't get it...

245
00:13:45,916 --> 00:13:46,958
Tokiha!

246
00:13:49,083 --> 00:13:54,041
It's easy to talk about it.
Wanting to help somebody.

247
00:13:54,125 --> 00:13:55,791
Saying you're doing it
for their sake.

248
00:13:55,875 --> 00:13:57,208
