249
00:13:58,916 --> 00:14:00,416
[YUICHI]
But if you ask me...

250
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:02,166
...when it comes
right down to it,

251
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:05,375
it's not your responsibilities
that matter the most.

252
00:14:05,458 --> 00:14:07,291
