260
00:14:19,791 --> 00:14:21,708
[SHIHO]
You're terrible, Brother.

261
00:14:21,791 --> 00:14:22,958
You lied.

262
00:14:23,041 --> 00:14:25,125
I've waited so long...

263
00:14:26,875 --> 00:14:27,916
[BOTH gasp]

264
00:14:31,291 --> 00:14:32,291
[gasps]

265
00:14:32,375 --> 00:14:33,583
[NATSUKI]
Stop it!

266
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,916
[SHIZURU]
Huh?

267
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,625
Why are you...
doing this...?

268
00:14:37,708 --> 00:14:39,333
'Cause I realized.

269
00:14:39,416 --> 00:14:41,125
You and I are a lot alike.

270
00:14:41,208 --> 00:14:42,250
Uh, wha...?

271
00:14:48,416 --> 00:14:49,541
[SHIZURU]
Don't do that.

272
00:14:49,625 --> 00:14:51,208
--[NATSUKI gasps]
--Just let it be.

273
00:14:51,291 --> 00:14:52,541
[NATSUKI gasps]

274
00:14:52,625 --> 00:14:55,625
Leave the beautiful there
flowers for everyone.

275
00:14:55,708 --> 00:14:57,083
They won't live too long,

276
00:14:57,166 --> 00:15:00,291
so they're doing their best
to bloom before they die.

277
00:15:01,416 --> 00:15:05,000
Do you wanna know the reason
why I didn't end up like Nao?

278
00:15:05,083 --> 00:15:09,166
It's because you and
the others were there for me.

279
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:12,625
I should've realized
it a lot sooner.

280
00:15:12,708 --> 00:15:14,416
Now I'm certain.

281
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,500
The person I love most...

282
00:15:23,250 --> 00:15:28,541
Oh, Natsuki... I'm relieved.
You've regained your strength.

283
00:15:28,625 --> 00:15:30,625
Just a little while ago...

284
00:15:30,708 --> 00:15:34,916
...I went and destroyed the
headquarters of District 1.

285
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:36,458
There are still
a few loose ends,

286
00:15:36,541 --> 00:15:38,416
like their affiliated
organizations,

287
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:42,250
so I need you to wait
just a little longer.

288
00:15:42,333 --> 00:15:45,166
You do belong to me, after all.

289
00:15:48,791 --> 00:15:50,375
[NATSUKI]
Shizuru!

290
00:15:52,791 --> 00:15:54,250
Shizuru...

291
00:15:54,333 --> 00:15:56,625
[NAO sobbing]
Why did this happen to me?!

292
00:15:56,708 --> 00:15:58,625
[sobs]
No...

293
00:15:58,708 --> 00:16:00,625
Mama!

294
00:16:00,708 --> 00:16:01,541
[sobbing]

295
00:16:01,625 --> 00:16:03,500
The fate of the HiME...

296
00:16:03,583 --> 00:16:06,666
I'm not going to let
fear get to me.

297
00:16:06,750 --> 00:16:08,833
I'm not... Mai.

298
00:16:13,250 --> 00:16:14,208
Mai!

299
00:16:14,291 --> 00:16:18,583
Hey. Brother.
Was that kiss a lie?

300
00:16:18,666 --> 00:16:20,875
And all your kindness?

301
00:16:20,958 --> 00:16:23,916
The fact you came
to see me every day?

302
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,083
Was it all just a big lie?

303
00:16:26,166 --> 00:16:27,208
[YUICHI]
Shiho, listen to me!

304
00:16:27,291 --> 00:16:29,083
I don't want to hear it!

305
00:16:29,166 --> 00:16:30,375
[snarls]

306
00:16:30,458 --> 00:16:31,541
It's all your fault!

307
00:16:31,625 --> 00:16:34,583
--[MAI gasps]
--So please, just go!

308
00:16:34,666 --> 00:16:35,875
Disappear...

309
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:40,208
[flute whistles]

310
00:16:43,833 --> 00:16:45,041
[roars]

311
00:16:45,125 --> 00:16:46,291
Shiho!

312
00:16:48,083 --> 00:16:49,125
[MAI grunts]

313
00:16:50,833 --> 00:16:51,875
[gasps]

314
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:55,125
[gasps]
No way...

315
00:16:55,208 --> 00:16:56,458
[SHIHO]
Don't try to run away!

316
00:16:56,541 --> 00:16:59,666
I want you to suffer
the same fate as that frog!

317
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:01,208
[MAI] You're the one
that defeated Akira!

318
00:17:01,291 --> 00:17:02,958
You killed Takumi!

319
00:17:03,041 --> 00:17:04,416
I had no choice.

320
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:06,666
Brother only seemed to
be interested in you.

321
00:17:06,750 --> 00:17:07,791
[gasps]

322
00:17:09,166 --> 00:17:10,458
Kagutsuchi!

323
00:17:13,916 --> 00:17:15,666
It wasn't me, then?

324
00:17:15,750 --> 00:17:16,791
In that case...

325
00:17:16,875 --> 00:17:17,958
[growls]

326
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,333
--Kagutsu--!
--[YUICHI] Tokiha!

327
00:17:26,416 --> 00:17:28,166
--[gasps]
--Shiho, you too!

328
00:17:28,250 --> 00:17:30,750
Stop this! I beg you!

329
00:17:30,833 --> 00:17:32,250
[NAGI] You'll have
to risk the one thing

330
00:17:32,333 --> 00:17:33,750
that's most important to you.

331
00:17:33,833 --> 00:17:34,666
[gasps]

332
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:37,666
[gasps]
Brother... No...

333
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:41,208
Brother belongs to me!
I fell in love with him first!

334
00:17:41,291 --> 00:17:44,250
He's all that I've ever wanted!

335
00:17:44,333 --> 00:17:45,583
[MAI]
You've gotta realize!

336
00:17:45,666 --> 00:17:48,291
No matter which one of us
is defeated, Tate will--

337
00:17:48,375 --> 00:17:49,875
--[SHIHO] Why?!
--[gasps]

338
00:17:49,958 --> 00:17:53,916
Why did you have to fall
in love with Brother?!

339
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,833
It's not like I
understand it myself!

340
00:17:56,916 --> 00:17:57,833
But...

341
00:17:57,916 --> 00:18:00,458
[growls]
You liar!

342
00:18:00,541 --> 00:18:01,833
Liar!

343
00:18:04,708 --> 00:18:05,583
[MAI]
Huh? Ah!

344
00:18:05,666 --> 00:18:06,708
[YUICHI]
Tokiha!

345
00:18:07,875 --> 00:18:08,916
[NATSUKI]
Mai!

346
00:18:11,208 --> 00:18:13,333
Shiho? No...

347
00:18:15,041 --> 00:18:15,583
[SHIHO gasps]

348
00:18:15,666 --> 00:18:17,625
[shrieks, grunts]

349
00:18:17,708 --> 00:18:19,333
Shiho!

350
00:18:19,416 --> 00:18:20,875
[MAI]
No! Kagutsuchi!

351
00:18:20,958 --> 00:18:22,250
[YUICHI pants]

352
00:18:24,166 --> 00:18:26,791
[SHIHO whimpers]

353
00:18:26,875 --> 00:18:28,416
I knew it...

354
00:18:28,500 --> 00:18:30,791
You... did come for me...

355
00:18:38,583 --> 00:18:40,291
Remember what day it is?

356
00:18:40,375 --> 00:18:42,416
It's special.

357
00:18:42,500 --> 00:18:45,791
This is the anniversary
of the first day we met.

358
00:18:51,750 --> 00:18:52,791
[gasps]

359
00:18:54,625 --> 00:18:56,166
[MAI gasps]

360
00:18:56,250 --> 00:18:59,166
It's me... My fault...

361
00:18:59,250 --> 00:19:02,458
[SHIHO]
Brother... M-My beloved Brother!

362
00:19:02,541 --> 00:19:04,083
Brother!

363
00:19:04,166 --> 00:19:07,375
Oh, man... I was wrong...

364
00:19:07,458 --> 00:19:09,625
All this time, I thought
that I understood

365
00:19:09,708 --> 00:19:12,041
what my true feelings were...

366
00:19:12,125 --> 00:19:13,166
[sighs]

367
00:19:15,041 --> 00:19:17,583
[YUICHI]
Tokiha! Shoot down that monster!

368
00:19:17,666 --> 00:19:19,000
--[gasps]
--Do it!

369
00:19:19,083 --> 00:19:20,875
I've hurt both of you
way too much!

370
00:19:20,958 --> 00:19:23,541
No! I can't do that!

371
00:19:23,625 --> 00:19:26,000
--[roaring]
--[gasps]

372
00:19:26,083 --> 00:19:26,958
[gasping]

373
00:19:27,041 --> 00:19:28,458
Mai!

374
00:19:28,541 --> 00:19:31,166
[REITO] The most powerful
opponent yet will come for Mai.

375
00:19:31,250 --> 00:19:34,666
And when that happens, you will
be the one to defeat it.

376
00:19:39,875 --> 00:19:42,666
I'm sorry, Tate...

377
00:19:42,750 --> 00:19:44,000
Mai!

378
00:19:47,208 --> 00:19:48,041
Mikoto!

379
00:19:48,125 --> 00:19:50,250
[shrieks]

380
00:19:54,375 --> 00:19:55,875
[gasps]

381
00:19:55,958 --> 00:19:57,625
[growls]

382
00:19:57,708 --> 00:20:00,083
Mikoto...
How could you do this?!

383
00:20:00,166 --> 00:20:02,791
It's an order...
from my brother.

384
00:20:02,875 --> 00:20:05,000
[MAI panting]

385
00:20:05,083 --> 00:20:06,125
[gasps]

386
00:20:07,375 --> 00:20:08,416
[gasps]

387
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:14,958
[YUICHI]
Mikoto... Thanks for doing it...

388
00:20:15,041 --> 00:20:16,208
Really...

389
00:20:20,125 --> 00:20:22,708
Now you and Shiho will
no longer have to fight...

390
00:20:22,791 --> 00:20:23,541
Agh!

391
00:20:23,625 --> 00:20:24,958
[gasps]

392
00:20:25,041 --> 00:20:29,583
Damn! I... hate to admit it...
but... dying is scary...

393
00:20:29,666 --> 00:20:30,541
Tate!

394
00:20:30,625 --> 00:20:31,875
--[YUICHI groans]
--[MAI sobs]

395
00:20:31,958 --> 00:20:35,416
Wait, Tate! I've still
got so much to say!

396
00:20:35,500 --> 00:20:37,916
I haven't even
told you how I feel!

397
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,625
[sobs]

398
00:20:39,708 --> 00:20:42,708
--Huh...?
--Tate! No, please!

399
00:20:42,791 --> 00:20:45,875
[fading]
Listen to me!

400
00:20:45,958 --> 00:20:47,916
[inaudible]

401
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:49,791
I'm sorry.

402
00:20:49,875 --> 00:20:52,250
Mai... I can't hear anymore...

403
00:20:52,333 --> 00:20:56,708
[inaudible]

404
00:20:58,125 --> 00:20:59,291
[YUICHI sighs]

405
00:21:17,541 --> 00:21:18,583
Yuichi...

406
00:21:25,041 --> 00:21:26,583
[NATSUKI whimpers]

407
00:21:26,666 --> 00:21:27,750
[gasps]

408
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:32,833
[NATSUKI]
Mai!

409
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:34,333
Mai?

410
00:21:34,416 --> 00:21:35,500
[MAI grunts]

411
00:21:36,958 --> 00:21:38,708
[whimpers]

412
00:21:41,208 --> 00:21:42,541
[MAI sobs]

413
00:21:42,625 --> 00:21:44,541
[screams]

414
00:21:44,625 --> 00:21:50,833
[wailing, sobbing]

415
00:21:50,916 --> 00:21:55,125
--[MIKOTO whimpers]
--[wailing continues]

416
00:21:57,583 --> 00:21:59,125
[REITO]
Tate, I'm impressed.

417
00:21:59,208 --> 00:22:01,750
I was expecting--and even
hoping--that you'd suffer

418
00:22:01,833 --> 00:22:05,708
a far more humiliating,
pathetic end.

419
00:22:05,791 --> 00:22:08,666
[NAGI] Still, everything's going
according to plan, right?

420
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:10,958
Mai's lost the most precious
person in her life,

421
00:22:11,041 --> 00:22:14,291
and there's no way that Mikoto
could ever return to her side.

422
00:22:14,375 --> 00:22:15,625
Correct.

423
00:22:15,708 --> 00:22:18,750
Now all of our careful
preparations are complete.

424
00:22:22,208 --> 00:22:24,041
[REITO]
It is finally coming...

425
00:22:24,125 --> 00:22:26,000
...the moment of destiny.

426
00:23:58,041 --> 00:23:59,458
[YUICHI]
What did you say before?

427
00:23:59,541 --> 00:24:00,708
[MAI]
You didn't hear it?!

428
00:24:00,791 --> 00:24:02,791
[YUICHI]
Nope, run it by me again.

429
00:24:02,875 --> 00:24:04,500
[MAI]
I can't, it's embarrassing.

430
00:24:04,583 --> 00:24:05,875
[YUICHI]
Jeez!

431
00:24:05,958 --> 00:24:08,333
I won't be able to rest
in peace unless you tell me.

432
00:24:08,416 --> 00:24:10,166
[MAI]
Then I'll never say it again!

433
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:11,208
Hmph!

